{
  "stem": "21626.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we also had shortages; and you know, apart from us, as I said, being separated from our parents.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was this that was very difficult to contend with.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One of the masters-- because most of Czechoslovakia was liberated-- this was by agreement between Churchill and-- and the-- and the Americans and Stalin-- that the Russians would liberate Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because of this, of course, the-- the Russians were in vogue.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they exploited this fact.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Russian had to be taught in all the schools, and had been since Prague was liberated, which was in the spring of last year.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And of course, I knew no Russian.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I had a merciless Russian teacher who punished me and derided me at every turn, because I found it difficult to catch up quickly with-- with the language; and sneered at me in such a manner.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When I was trying to make a life with my aunt, who was a [SIGHS] chronic depressant, for whom life became a burden because she survived, and filled with guilt because she buried so many; and as a 16, 17-year-old, you know, I had to cope with that.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was a very difficult.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then coping with the antagonism I got at school made it impossible.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And one day, I came back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And by then, actually, we'd moved out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I managed to get the housing office to let us have one room in what used to be my father's flat.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was the room-- the tiniest backroom, sunless room, in which our maid used to live.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we had that in the tiny little scullery where there was a tap-- cold water tap.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We weren't allowed to use the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were allowed to use the toilet of what was her flat.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
